//! job; duplicating it here would be scope creep, not a second check). It
//! cannot prove ggen's own SPARQL/Tera pipeline is bug-free in some absolute
//! sense -- only that, on the sync run that (re)generated this file, the
//! live ontology and the checked-in generated artifacts said the same
